The paper deals with object detection and classification in images, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a framework that improves the learning effectiveness of neural network models, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of image segmentation and chroma-key techniques also involves graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) aspects.
